### 1. Login as User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### 2. Create BuyMe Request (User)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/buyme
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "productName": "Nike Air Zoom Pegasus",
  "productLink": "https://www.nike.com/product/air-zoom-pegasus",
  "color": "Black",
  "size": "42",
  "quantity": 1,
  "deliveryCountry": "Saudi Arabia",
  "shippingMethod": "Express",
  "notes": "Please double-check authenticity",
  "image": "https://example.com/shoe.jpg"
}

### 3. Get My BuyMe Requests (User)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/buyme/my
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 4. Get Single BuyMe Request by ID (User or Admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/buyme/{{buymeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 5. Update BuyMe Request (User or Admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/buyme/{{buymeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "status": "purchased",
  "notes": "Purchased from Nike Turkey"
}

### 6. Delete BuyMe Request (User or Admin)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/buyme/{{buymeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 7. Get All BuyMe Requests (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/buyme
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
